; =============================================================================
; test_dispatch.mon — VICE monitor commands for dispatch unit tests
; =============================================================================
; Usage:
;   make test_dispatch
; Or manually:
;   x64sc -autostart tests/test_dispatch.prg -moncommands tests/test_dispatch.mon
;
; When the CPU hits td_spin (end of all tests), the VICE monitor opens.
; In the monitor, type:
;   mem $0600 $0600     — shows pass count (08 = all 8 tests passed)
;   go                  — resume (loops forever at td_spin)
; =============================================================================

loadsym tests/test_dispatch.vs
break td_spin
go
